# SEO & ACCESSIBILITY (A11Y) STANDARDS
- Semantic HTML: Strict header hierarchy (Single H1, Logical H2-H3). 
- Metadata: Auto-generate optimized <title> and <meta description> for every page.
- Images: Force `loading="lazy"` and `decoding="async"`. 
- Descriptions: Always include descriptive `alt` tags for photos and `aria-label` for icons/buttons.
- Performance: Use `WebP` or compressed `PNG`. Ensure high Contrast Ratio for pastel text vs background.
